The files that we have are scanned pdfs. They have typed letters, cursive, blur pages, etc.    
So, we attempted to add more fonts and train tesseract on those   
This would improve the results obtained through teserract for optical character recognition   

<b>Steps to train tesseract:<b>
The article [here](http://michaeljaylissner.com/posts/2012/02/11/adding-new-fonts-to-tesseract-3-ocr-engine) explains the process of training tesseract  
